.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, strawberry, zucchini
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, musician, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, salsa, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, dutch, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, train, motorbike, car
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the american##1
 2. the dutch is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the musician##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of soul is between the analyst and the person eating zucchini##2
 7. the german is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 9. the german is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the firefighter is the person driving the car##1
11. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
12. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the fan of salsa is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | milk     | cola        | fanta    |
| Food          | strawberry     | radish   | blueberry   | zucchini |
| Job           | security-guard | analyst  | firefighter | musician |
| Music-Genre   | pop            | salsa    | soul        | ambient  |
| Nationality   | dutch          | american | german      | british  |
| Transport           | train          | quad-bike     | car      | motorbike      |

