.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, photography, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, electrician, manager
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, satire, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, german, indian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, sunflower, aconite
 1. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is the indian##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the analyst##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the french##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is between the electrician and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the electrician is the german##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who growsaconite and the german##2
10. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
11. the manager is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | milk        | coffee      | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Hobby         | photography | board-games | skydiving   | dancing   |
| Job           | electrician | manager     | chef        | analyst   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | thriller    | documentary | satire    |
| Nationality   | german      | french      | indian      | brazilian |
| Flower           | orchid      | bellflower    | aconite       | sunflower  |

