.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, tea
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, carrot, kale, kiwi
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, yellow, turquise, white
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, metal, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, german, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hamster, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is between the american and the owner of the goldfish##2
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes white##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
13. the fan of funk is between the person who likes grey and the owner of the ferret##2
14. the person who likes white is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea      | hot-chocolate | lemonade       | mirinda   |
| Food          | carrot   | kale          | kiwi           | blueberry |
| Color           | grey     | yellow    | white | turquise     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | funk          | gospel         | metal     |
| Nationality   | dutch    | american      | nigerian       | german    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | hamster       | ferret         | goldfish  |

