.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, peach, pear, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, puzzles, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, social-worker, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, satire, time-travel
4 different games are played: go, billiard, scrabble, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the social-worker##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is between the writer and the bartender##2
 3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fisherman##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person driving the car and the person playing billiard##2
 7. the person driving the trike is between the person playing go and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the writer##1
11. the fisherman is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
13. the person playing scrabble is the person eating artichoke##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Food          | radish     | pear        | peach         | artichoke   |
| Hobby         | baking     | puzzles     | filmmaking    | woodworking |
| Job           | fisherman  | writer      | social-worker | bartender   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | time-travel | satire        | crime       |
| Game   | poker    | billiard     | go    | scrabble     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | trike       | train         | car         |

