.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lime, peach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, climbing, handball
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, electrician, manager, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, family, western
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, russian, thai
 1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the manager##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the mexican is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the accountant##1
 7. the electrician is on the right of the accountant##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is the russian##1
10. the person eating peach is on the right of the electrician##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
12. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person drinking water and the manager##2
13. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | water       | fanta         |
| Food          | cabbage | grapefruit  | lime        | peach         |
| Sport         | climbing | water-polo | soccer     | handball   |
| Job           | manager | accountant  | electrician | social-worker |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | western     | drama       | documentary   |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani   | thai        | mexican       |

